# Refine Dimensions and Sensitivity Plan

## Goal Description
Expand the interactive area of the piano keys and find a balanced sensitivity setting.

## User Review Required
None.

## Proposed Changes
### files
#### [MODIFY] [app.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/app.py)
- **Dimensions**:
    - Increase `piano_h` from `100` to `150`. This makes the keys tall again, easier to target.
- **Sensitivity**:
    - Set `VELOCITY_THRESHOLD` to `0.10`.
        - 0.08 was "too sensitive".
        - 0.15 was "very high".
        - 0.10 should be the "Goldilocks" zone.

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Run the app.
- Verify keys are larger/taller.
- Verify striking feels natural (not too hard, not too spammy).
